{"tid":1365433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[攻略] 元朗國飲食地圖","createTime":"2019-07-25T15:43:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T18:31:23.000Z","uid":18824,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bf0dfc8b094ca0279970912182944df50ee83d55","tid":1365433,"uid":18824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:43:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">熱烈慶祝</span>元朗7月21號立國，為咗促進該國經濟，進入元朗旅遊時不妨參考以下地圖，不過去之前記得向當地鄉議局整簽證。<br />\n為咗響應元朗飲食節，大家記得<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">12點</span></span>就好到<span style=\"color: red;\">水邊圍遊樂場</span>啦（朗屏至水邊圍路線已提供），如果唔係去到夜晚啲美食就俾人食晒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/60mBiB5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F60mBiB5.jpg&h=29b1c21f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">如何使用本地圖</div></span></span><br />\n請先download google map &amp; google drive<br />\nStep1 打開連結<br />\nStep2 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wkiPCgS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwkiPCgS.jpg&h=6845e7f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如沒google drive<br />\nStep1 直接開啟連結<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">地圖更新!!!!!</span></div></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n現時只開放飲食版本，如有需求才會加開(個人不建議在元朗篇勇武)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">逃脫版</span><br />\n有需要時開放予車手和大眾<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">飲食路線頭段</span> </div></span><br />\n1.起點接近水邊圍民居<br />\n2.元朗警署 <br />\n3.元朗廣場 (三層 算大)，有吉野家 老麥，有天橋連接朗屏站<br />\n4.喜利商埸到開心商埸中間都係唐樓<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中段</span></div></span><br />\n1.開心廣場三層開放，可以作哨<br />\n對面係實惠賣傢私有兩層<br />\n2.大馬路麥當勞 24小時+二層<br />\n3.打後400米都係唐樓<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">尾段</span></div></span><br />\n1.天橋連接雞地同大馬路<br />\nPs 雞地一帶都有牛屎<br />\n2.yohomall 2 連接元朗站，北面就係重牛屎地帶<br />\n3.yohomall 1可經天橋往雞地<br />\n<br />\n廁所 <br />\n飲食行路線無咩廁所，去定先!!!!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">元朗特色美食</div></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">頭段</div></span><br />\n1.漁民麵館，花膠湯麵好好味，行過去好近<br />\n2.醉權，近朗屏站，大家可以食咗先集合，專系食醉雞<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">中段</div></span><br />\n3.天奴豬扒，食咗好多年<br />\n4.永年士多，係飲食路線頭段以南，有可能撞到發哥<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">尾段</div></span><br />\n6.田中壽司，唔知點解好出名<br />\n7.其奧花生糖，多年老字號，好似已經傳咗兩代，<br />\n每日新鮮製造<br />\n8.燒賣皇后，係花生糖隔離，唔知因為啲咩好出名，不過燒賣有質素<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">區內景點</span><br />\n<br />\n1.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">南邊圍福德堂(私人地方)</span></span> lv1 to lv5<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">參觀難道 lv1<br />\n參觀意義 lv5</div> <br />\n<br />\n對面係元朗站，非常接近飲食路線終點，離馬路近，前往參觀不需經過複雜的圍村陣，方便離開，大家不妨整個連儂堂！[/right]<br />\n<br />\n2.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屏山鄉事會</span></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">參觀難道 lv2<br />\n參觀意義 lv3</div><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n接近飲食路線開始，在元朗廣場後方，和兵營較遠，十分建議遊客前往<br />\n<br />\n3.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">十八鄉鄉事會</span></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">參觀難道 lv1<br />\n參觀意義 lv3</div><br />\n<br />\n接近飲食路線尾段，在元朗站旁，容易<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不建議的景點</span><br />\n1.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">西邊圍村公所(私人地方)</span></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">參觀難道 lv5<br />\n參觀意義 lv4<br />\n</div><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有馬路直入，但兩旁圍屋，地勢複雜，就算有經驗飲食家都不宜進入<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">牛屎出怪點:</span><br />\n1.<span style=\"font-size: large;\">馬田村</span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">出怪數量 lv2 40人</div><br />\n飲食路線南部 元朗圖書館南部，接近民居，哨兵容易觀察<br />\n2.<span style=\"font-size: large;\">下攸田村</span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">出怪數量 lv2 40人</div><br />\n飲食路線南部，近民居，哨兵容易觀察<br />\n3.<span style=\"font-size: large;\">南邊圍</span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">出怪數量 lv4 200人up</div><br />\n4.<span style=\"font-size: large;\">西邊圍</span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">出怪數量 lv4 200人up</div><br />\n5.<span style=\"font-size: large;\">元朗工業村</span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">出怪數量 lv3  60人</div><br />\n6.<span style=\"font-size: large;\">屏山</span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">出怪數量 lv3 60人</div><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>離開路線</span><br />\n元朗站終點(入夜後很大可能狗方設防)<br />\n1.港鐵<br />\n2.元朗站對面線巴士站往荃灣大埔港島<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">危險路線</span></span><br />\n1.步行往天水圍，兩旁村屋<br />\n2.南生圍，不解釋<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">整合</div></span></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">戰略</span></div><br />\n細良提醒: 去元朗係反黑。不是光復!! <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1356278/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1356278/page/1</a><br />\n入元朗唔係為咗報仇燒村 勇武派絕不能主動出擊 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1353244/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1353244/page/1</a><br />\n如果我係警，27號可以一舖收哂勇武派皮 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1352880/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1352880/page/1</a><br />\n覺得光復元朗唔係對準政權 = 膚淺+ON9 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1352326/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1352326/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n元朗條遊行路線其實真係要做多d風險評估<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1357515/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1357515/page/1</a><br />\n727 光復元朗嘅潛在風險<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1357362/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1357362/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"110e74fad34d1b439396647419c912faf33c1407","tid":1365433,"uid":18824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:44:22.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"16beac5cfef498b143c742d9ec16bb421e0b79cc","tid":1365433,"uid":18824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:51:29.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"016bbe2179e93eba318e6d6da18aea222e7667a5","tid":1365433,"uid":18824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:56:34.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"19a861af34b19973e521c0d04e19d7a5a756c90e","tid":1365433,"uid":9824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:59:03.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"ffe69e1fa48d86675522097b8ca45249418fb484","tid":1365433,"uid":282891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:31:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KtvuD77.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKtvuD77.png&h=4ae4ecc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">藍色 購物</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃色 買餸</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">紫色 文娛</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">紅色 掃街</span></span><br />\n<br />\n餐廳介紹<br />\n- 大棠路 <br />\n勝利牛丸 嘉麗園 <br />\n- 又新街 <br />\n恆香餅家 燒賣皇后 串皇 發記粥品 <br />\n韓點 咖喱至尊<br />\n- 教育路 <br />\n小鍋米線 B仔 士林牛肉麵 永年士多 酒泉日本料理<br />\n- 建德街 <br />\n萬芳冰室 過橋麵檔<br />\n- 安寧路 <br />\n大榮華酒家 小窩米線 豬小姐<br />\n- 馬田路<br />\n韓舍 薩利呀 (其實冇乜嘢食 純粹疏導人流)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab91a4c0e9f504200704bc9bd4b6040b5a538a46","tid":1365433,"uid":18824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T18:21:55.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"a2f27f017987eade631e4a931ea41d1537e5ddbf","tid":1365433,"uid":18824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T18:31:23.000Z","msg":"我無野講"}]}